html: _Cimilik_. Sp.2.112(VRI): _Cimilik nma sudhdiparikammakatya bhmiy vanurakkhaattha kat hoti, ta heh pattharitv upari kaasraka pattharanti_A _cimilik_ is made to protect the color of a floor that has been plastered, etc. It is spread out underneath, with a straw-mat spread out on top. {}
<dd>_Akappiyakata hoti_, literally, It is done with what is not allowable. The it, both here and below, refers to the ceremony of making it allowable, and the what refers to the food. {}
